Caballo's free horse market app offers convenient mobile access to all horse classified ads in the online horse market. If you‘re either looking for a specific horse or just want to browse the horses for sale: you‘ll find numerous up-to-date horses for sale from breeders and individuals from all over europe.

How it works:

Choose from one of the existing categories in the horse market or describe what you are looking for with help of the search tab. The app will give you an overview of all matching horses.

For any horse you may look up further details such as a description, photos, videos, abilities, pedigree and its approximate location on a map. If you are interested in a horse, just call the seller directly via the app or leave him a message.

Horses of interest may be saved to your favorite list on your device can be found easily later and are even available without an internet connection.

Questions or comments?

Contact us directly from the app via 'More' - 'Feedback'. You may also send us an email to support@caballo-horsemarket.com of course.
